Art and Dress Along the Silk Road at the UNT Art Gallery in 2012. Previous exhibitions were produced in conjunction with the Crow Collection of Asian Art (Yeohlee: Design for Now, 2009), and the Meadows Museum, the Dallas Museum of Art, and the Kimbell Art Museum. To browse the TFC's holdings, visit the UNT Digital Library. If you would like to be notified of updates, periodic electronic newsletters, details on current and upcoming exhibitions, events and more from the Texas Fashion Collection, click the button below to be added to our mailing list. Sign Up for Updates We will not share, sell, rent, swap or authorize any third party to use your email address for commercial purposes without your permission.If after subscribing you no longer wish to receive updates or newsletters, follow the "unsubscribe" instructions located near the bottom of each email. Visit Us Texas Fashion Collection 405 S. Welch Street, Suite 102 University of North Texas Denton, Texas 76203 Mail Us University of North Texas College of Visual Arts & Design 1155 Union Circle #305100 Denton, TX 76203 Contact Us (940) 565-2732 tfc@unt.edu Technical issues? Site last updated on May 09, 2017 Disclaimer| AA/EOE/ADA| Privacy| Electronic Accessibility| State of Texas Online| Emergency Preparedness| THECB Online Resume System Student Consumer Information| UNT Compliance Hotline| Governors Committee on People with Disabilities| Texas Veterans Portal| UNT Home Site last updated on May 09, 2017 | Important Links 